        "text": "We now compute ABF = (AF/AC) [ABC| =2, [ABR] = (BR/BF) ABF] = z/2, analogously [BCS = [CAT] = z/2, and RST] = ABC - ABR - [BCS - (CAT]| = 11-32/21=2-3V5",
